<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Jadwal Lengkap Perjalanan KAI</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/home.css">
    <style>
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        th, td {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        th {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
        }
        tr:nth-child(even) {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .intro-text {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="navbar">
        <div class="navbar-left">
            <h1 class="navbar-title">Jadwal Lengkap Perjalanan KAI</h1>
        </div>
        <nav>
            <a href="/home">Beranda</a>
            <a href="/booking">Pesan Tiket</a>
            <a href="/logout" class="btn-logout">Logout</a>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <div class="container">
            <p class="intro-text">Kami menyediakan jadwal perjalanan kereta api yang lengkap untuk berbagai rute populer di Indonesia:</p>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Rute</th>
                        <th>Waktu Keberangkatan</th>
                        <th>Waktu Tiba</th>
                        <th>Durasi Perjalanan</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Jakarta - Bandung</td>
                        <td>08:00</td>
                        <td>11:00</td>
                        <td>3 jam</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Surabaya - Yogyakarta</td>
                        <td>14:00</td>
                        <td>18:00</td>
                        <td>4 jam</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Medan - Kualanamu</td>
                        <td>07:30</td>
                        <td>08:00</td>
                        <td>30 menit</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Semarang - Solo</td>
                        <td>09:00</td>
                        <td>10:45</td>
                        <td>1 jam 45 menit</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 Kereta Api Indonesia. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
